# Smart AI-Based Vision System using ESP32 & Edge Impulse

## Overview

This project is an AI-powered embedded vision system built using ESP32, Edge Impulse, and TensorFlow Lite. The system is capable of capturing sensor or image-based input, processing it using machine learning models, and performing intelligent real-time predictions on edge devices.

The project combines embedded systems, machine learning, and IoT technologies to create a lightweight and efficient AI solution suitable for real-world applications.

---

# Features

✨ Real-time AI inference on ESP32

✨ Edge Impulse model integration

✨ TensorFlow Lite support

✨ Lightweight embedded deployment 

✨ Sensor/Image data processing  

✨ Optimized for edge computing 

✨ Arduino IDE compatible  

✨ Cross-platform development support  


---

# Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |

|------------|---------|

| Python | Data processing & utilities |

| ESP32 | Embedded hardware platform |

| Arduino IDE | Firmware development |

| Edge Impulse | ML model training |

| TensorFlow Lite | Edge AI inference |

| Jupyter Notebook | Model experimentation |

| VS Code | Development environment |

