# Project Structure

```bash
├── data/                     # Dataset files

├── datasets/                 # Training datasets

├── edge-impulse-sdk/         # Edge Impulse generated SDK

├── models/                   # Trained ML models

├── notebooks/                # Jupyter notebooks

├── src/                      # Source code

├── build/                    # Build files

├── dist/                     # Distribution files

├── README.md

├── requirements.txt

└── .gitignore
